0:03:52.580,0:03:58.740
uye yakange asingakwanisi kurara pasi; Ndakanga ndiri mumarwadzo akanyanya.

0:03:58.740,0:04:00.380
Mushure maizvozvo...

0:04:00.380,0:04:06.840
Saka, kungoti tijekese munin'ina - pakarepo mushure mokunge wasangana nepfambi, wakadhakwa ne doro,

0:04:06.840,0:04:12.520
kusvuta, re chimangwana nhengo yako yakamira zvachose ichiramba kurara pasi

0:04:12.520,0:04:14.380
