Mushure mekunge chiremba andiudza kuti ndaifanira ku oparetwa ...

0:04:38.360,0:04:42.700
Panguva iyoyo, ndakanga ndichirwadziwa uye ndakanga ndisina sarudzo.

0:04:42.700,0:04:51.700
Ndakarara pamubhedha ndichimirira kuti vaite zvavaida kuita.

0:04:51.700,0:05:00.040
Apo amai vangu vakauya, ndakavaudza zvaive zvataurwa nachiremba.

0:05:00.040,0:05:13.340
