0:05:40.700,0:05:45.760
asi nekuda kwekuradziwa kwawaiitwa, wakabvumirana nazvo uye wakabhukwa kuti uitwe oparesheni,

0:05:45.760,0:05:48.840
apo amai vako vakauya kuzosangana newe kuchipatara?

0:05:48.840,0:05:50.780
hongu

0:05:50.780,0:05:53.280
Saka, shure kweizvozvo ...

0:05:53.280,0:06:05.980
Vakatoita kuti ndibvume kuti ndaigona kuzvisarudzira ndega pachagu kana ndaida kuoparetwa kana kwete

0:06:05.980,0:06:14.160
Ndakazovaudza kuti sezvo amai vangu vakanga varipo, ndaizoita sezvaive varaira.

0:06:14.160,0:06:20.780
Ndaizoenda chero uko amai vangu vandiendesa.

0:06:20.780,0:06:28.540
Zuva iroro, ivo vakanyora zvinyorwa pamusoro pedu nebhiro tsvuku pachinzvimbo cheye bhuruu -

0:06:28.540,0:06:35.300
nokuti vakanga vakatsamwa - ini handizivi kuti sei.

0:06:35.300,0:06:41.440
Takaenda kumba uye zuva rakatevera, takauya ku Lagos.

0:06:41.440,0:06:52.700
Musi wa 20 December, takasvika pa SCOAN.

0:06:52.700,0:06:58.640
Tinoda kunzwisisa; pawakasvika pa SCOAN, iwe wakanga uri mamiriro ezvinhu akaoma zvikuru, mumarwadzo makuru,

0:06:58.640,0:07:00.820
uye mu Porofita T.B. Joshua akakunyengeterera.

0:07:00.820,0:07:05.160
Iwe unogona here kutsanangura kwatiri chakaitika paakakunyengeterera iwe?

0:07:05.160,0:07:16.520
Paakandinyengeterera, ndakanzwa kufara uye ndakasunungurwa.

0:07:16.520,0:07:19.140
Zvose zvave zvazvinofanirwa kuve

0:07:19.140,0:07:23.560
Ndinonzwa sekacheche kachangozvarwa.

0:07:23.560,0:07:24.360
