0:07:24.360,0:07:28.260
Saka, takaona paakakunyengeterera iwe, wakawira pasi.

0:07:28.260,0:07:32.580
Unogona here kurondedzera zvaiitika mumuviri wako panguva iyoyo?

0:07:32.580,0:07:42.400
Paakaisa ruoko rwake pamusoro pangu, kutanga, ndakanzwa sokuti pane kupenya kwe mwenje pameso angu,

0:07:42.400,0:07:46.040
