0:07:46.040,0:07:50.840
Ndiri pasi, ndakanga ndisingazivi zvaiitika.

0:07:50.840,0:07:55.980
Pandakazo pengenuka zvakare ndichizviona ndiri pasi ndakaona kuti zvinhu zvose zvakanga zvadzokera kune masikiro azvo!

0:07:55.980,0:07:56.980
Rumbidzai Ishe!

0:07:56.980,0:08:00.340
Ameni. Ngatiisei maoko edu pamwechete kuna Jesu Kristu!

0:08:00.340,0:08:06.060
