hongu

0:08:43.820,0:08:47.640
Ameni, ngatiisei maoko edu pamwechete kuna Jesu Kristu.

0:08:47.640,0:08:52.160
Munin'ina, yave mwedzi yakawanda kubvira ipapo; Ingotiudza - zvinoreva here kuti panguva iyi yose

0:08:52.160,0:08:57.560
iwe wainge uchirarama hupenyu hwe masikirwo, hwakasununguka, usina marwadzo enhengo yakamira zvachose?

0:08:57.560,0:08:59.040
Hongu

