0:11:13.780,0:11:19.760
Zvaiita sokuti vakanga vachiedza kuzvivanza kubva kwandiri; vakanga vasingadi kuti ndizive chinetso chaicho.

0:11:19.760,0:11:23.840
Nemhaka yekurwadziwa kwaaiva nako, akabvumira kuti aoparetwe

0:11:23.840,0:11:28.640
