0:11:39.280,0:11:45.220
Havana kumutora kuimba ye oparesheni ndisati ndasvika.

0:11:45.220,0:11:52.720
Pandakasvika, ndakavaudza kuti kwete, mukomana uyu aisazo oparetwa.

0:11:52.720,0:11:56.360
Vakandibvunza kuti sei ini ndakati rutendo rwangu rwakanga rusiri muchipatara.

0:11:56.360,0:12:02.760
Kuna Mwari kuve ne kubwinya, ndakanzwa vanachiremba vachitaurirana pakati pavo

0:12:02.760,0:12:08.680
