0:12:12.360,0:12:16.780
Ndakabva ndaudza baba vake zvairehwa navanachiremba.

0:12:16.780,0:12:20.340
Akabvunza, "Sezvo mukomana ari kurwadziwa, toita sei?"

0:12:20.340,0:12:22.540
Ndakati kwete, kuti Mwari aizoita chimwe chinhu.

0:12:22.540,0:12:27.600
Ndakateterera; vakandiendesa kumutungamiriri mukuru wechipatara kuti andivimbise

0:12:27.600,0:12:30.380
kuti mukomana aifanira kuoparetwa.

0:12:30.380,0:12:33.920
Ndakavaudza kuti kutenda kwangu kwakanga kusiri muchipatara,

0:12:33.920,0:12:35.880
kuti vaifanira kundibvumira kutora mukomana kuchechi.

0:12:35.880,0:12:40.000
