0:12:40.000,0:12:43.440
Vakamuendesa kuimba yeku opareterwa kuti vamumanikidze kuti avhiyiwe.

0:12:43.440,0:12:47.820
Ndakamuona achibuda achiti, "Madhamu, sezvo imi ..." ...

0:12:47.820,0:12:53.380
Vakandipa rugwaro ndokundikumbira kuti ndiisayine.

0:12:53.380,0:13:00.520
Ndakati ini ndakaenda kuchikoro regai ndiverenge mazwi akanyorwa ndisati ndasaina.

