Ndinofanira kutenda Mwari nekuita kuti izvi zviitike.

0:17:16.840,0:17:20.740
Akauya uye isu takaita hurongwa.

0:17:20.740,0:17:24.220
Ndizvozvo chaizvo zvakaitika.

0:17:24.220,0:17:32.700
Ndinoda kutaura kuti akandikurudzira uye akakurudzira mhuri

0:17:32.700,0:17:37.520
nokuti isu takanga tavhiringidzika panguva iyoyo.

0:17:37.520,0:17:41.000
Saka, kamwe zvakare, tinogona kunzwisisa kuti mamiriro acho ezvinhu akaoma sei.

0:17:41.000,0:17:44.080
Kukudzwa ngakuve kuna Mwari kuti mwanakomana wenyu akauya ku SCOAN.

0:17:44.080,0:17:50.740
Changamire, imi mungati chii nezvekushandurwa kweupenyu hwake kuburikidza nemunamato wemu Porofita T.B. Joshua?

0:17:50.740,0:17:54.380
Paiva nekushandurwa, kwete chete nezvehutano

0:17:54.380,0:17:57.760
asi zvakare pamusoro peimwe yenyaya dzataisangana nadzo.

0:17:57.760,0:18:02.340
Pakarepo paakanyengetererwa, apo akagamuchira kuporeswa kwake,

0:18:02.340,0:18:05.600
akabva asimba uye zvose zvakabva zvapinda mugwara chairo

0:18:05.600,0:18:12.020
Paiva nezvimwe zvinhu izvo vakoma vake vakanga vasingakwanisi kuita iye, nomwoyo wose,

0:18:12.020,0:18:18.620
